cu.explanation_en: Setting the integrity algorithm to the unknown enum 'nia9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting the RF simulator model name to the unknown enum 'invalid' will cause the simulator initialization to fail and prevent the DU from starting properly.
du.explanation_zh: 將 RF 模擬器模型名稱設定為未知的枚舉值 'invalid'，會導致模擬器初始化失敗，並阻止 DU 正確啟動。
